{"tid":2081660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"體通天下暫停轉播英格蘭足總盃及德甲","createTime":"2020-06-27T11:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T16:08:22.000Z","uid":53391,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55932002795500970bea4be996e963d5cb69586d","tid":2081660,"uid":53391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"會員公告<br />\n<br />\n自德甲復賽以後，我司 與內容供應商於合同上的理解出現分歧及產生爭拗。我司近兩個月已不斷地與相關的供應商進行多番商討並作出不少讓步！ 唯近日供應商提出我司無法接受的不合理要求，故在極無奈的情況下我司決定暫停轉播英格蘭足總盃及德甲等足球賽事直至另行通知！<br />\n<br />\n對會員造成的影響我司表示萬二分抱歉。 並會對已購買有關足球會籍的會員作出補償及退款！詳情請留意往後的公告！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sports2worldhk/posts/893612911131603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsports2worldhk%2Fposts%2F893612911131603&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a993d44e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sports2worldhk/posts/893612911131603</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f576011d7e9430866fb53f95b47bc34d7c4a89","tid":2081660,"uid":228143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"德甲有鬼人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拜仁練習賽"},{"pid":"d8da623afa9b8588424b40322bbe92f6cf5ad2c4","tid":2081660,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"愛國就睇國足"},{"pid":"112076dd743019defa3cbee14122d561bc6ad215","tid":2081660,"uid":30319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:43:18.000Z","msg":"唔係執埋間公司咪偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b49fcf825e45b5120a61756d439e427c1bd54ee","tid":2081660,"uid":1823,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"@吉村xxx"},{"pid":"32f2f69737f196ea2710077fb82c9a403bc6007d","tid":2081660,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:46: